/------------ HYPHENS ---------------------------\


Tagging:

// Add a feature startbis, just after a sent:+ 
5> ? = | ?[toutmaj:~], ?[sent] | ?[!startbis=+] . 

// Add a feature endbis, to a sent:+
5> ?<sent> = | ?[toutmaj:~] | ?[!endbis=+]  .

// Add a feature endbis to the last word of a block
5> ? = ?[!endbis=+] | |.





